Can I use Retinol with Trubiom Pigmentation corrector cream?🤨

If you want to use both Retinol and Trubiom Pigmentation corrector cream, we recommend using them on alternate days and at a reduced frequency. For eg - If you typically use retinol 4x a week then reduce it to 2x a week instead ❤️😌

PS - The product may change its colour in due course. The discolouration is only an aesthetic condition and there is no safety concern, the efficacy remains intact ✌🏻
